Package: wortschatzR
Type: Package
Title: Wrappers around the REST API from the Leipzig Corpora Collection
Version: 0.2.2
Author: Tim Graf
Maintainer: Tim Graf <tim@tim-graf.de>
Description: Package can be used to automatically retrieve frequency data from Leipzig Wortschatz using a list of words. The code was partially adapted from valentin wagner (2016-07-13).
